{"tid":970464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"徵婚，我男找女，英籍，有房，在倫敦，先懷孕，後登記，保證留英","createTime":"2019-01-05T22:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T12:30:24.000Z","uid":163248,"like":43,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"60df2815f5eed0621663992e48e64bdb9b42c38b","tid":970464,"uid":163248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:27:21.000Z","msg":"因為現代避孕技術太先進了，先登記後懷孕這種傳統婚姻係對男方『最沒保障』嘅結婚方式。所以我係要求先懷孕後登記。只要一懷孕，我就會登記，立此為據。因為我係英國國籍，所以這個孩子在哪里出生都有英國國籍，也無論他／她媽媽是不是合法移民，這個孩子都有英國國籍。我係有足夠實力保證妳能留在英國同我一齊建立家庭。如果有想為身份而找我的女士，我都非常歡迎。因為我係要和妳建立家庭，所以你不想留英，我更緊張，如果妳不想留英，也不用聯繫我了。<br />\n<br />\n我在倫敦。有英國國藉。離過婚，沒小孩，想要小孩，有房，現在剛42歲。可以考慮我嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果您想找一起奮鬥的人。我相信我也合適。我正在自己做生意，也想有個幫手。<br />\n<br />\n我想找的人的條件：1，你是個女的。2，最好25歲，其他年齡都可以，但超過37就免了。3，願意生孩子，我係一定要孩子，如果不打算生孩子的，請不要打擾。4，如果不是近期內想結婚的，也請不要聯繫。5，學歷越高越好，但低的都可以聯繫我。6，歡迎沒有工作的女生聯繫我。如果妳已經有工作，請先想好妳是否願意「放棄工作來倫敦」才聯繫我，免得大家浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我再重申，我要先懷孕，再立刻登記。這是對雙方的最大保障。當然，如果妳覺得可以說服我先登記後懷孕，也可以聯繫我。或者妳是持開放心態，兩種情況都可以考慮，也歡迎聯繫我。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ybirds.com/Uploads/Class/20181203/472f55512e8c76788d5d0b103a657ce2c3ce7466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ybirds.com%2FUploads%2FClass%2F20181203%2F472f55512e8c76788d5d0b103a657ce2c3ce7466.jpg&h=58730cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉貼：<a href=\"https://www.ybirds.com/Home-CtgInfo-ctgInfoDetail-id-678527.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ybirds.com%2FHome-CtgInfo-ctgInfoDetail-id-678527.html&d=rCC6LyfnNA3Id4pBenNlATPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=db2300f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ybirds.com/Home-CtgInfo-ctgInfoDetail-id-678527.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大隻蛤拿隨街跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0b1c4ba7c19f0b45ebcfb10f28a5c09b4b0192","tid":970464,"uid":66943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:33:40.000Z","msg":"男的也能懷孕"},{"pid":"96c2b7d1fd109c718f75725b847b0ffa71f24012","tid":970464,"uid":130479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:37:28.000Z","msg":"呃蝦條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9567d4991ea38b35e40f52c51bfcf2f49cc7ae93","tid":970464,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"24<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b30ed2586b86d349ff84de88cc26903916a3c3","tid":970464,"uid":174432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"有咗三個月申唔申請得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (幫朋友問"},{"pid":"84237f16524b2ca528b480a0c7e8f0f4880ec1bf","tid":970464,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c2b7d1fd109c718f75725b847b0ffa71f24012","tid":970464,"uid":130479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T22:37:28.000Z","msg":"呃蝦條<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb222c74cf9746e1f85c2bdf74f86467a3e9344b","tid":970464,"uid":161098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"其實男人要溝女都好易啊，只有個發達國家嗰國籍離過婚都可以要求搵個細自己差唔多20歲+高學歷嘅女仔，仲要人地會話「好大隻蛤拿隨街跳」..."},{"pid":"d9198df1b2069fe6df794635f009770b7279328c","tid":970464,"uid":163248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84237f16524b2ca528b480a0c7e8f0f4880ec1bf","tid":970464,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c2b7d1fd109c718f75725b847b0ffa71f24012","tid":970464,"uid":130479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cite